serviceOrganisation.name: Australian Securities and Investments Commission
serviceOrganisation.description: ASIC is Australia’s corporate, markets and financial services regulator. We contribute to Australia’s economic reputation and wellbeing by ensuring that Australia’s financial markets are fair and transparent, supported by confident and informed investors and consumers.

serviceDimensions.name: Money Smart
serviceDimensions.description: You can check to see if your finances are under control, what areas need attention and simple steps to improve any gaps with this Moneysmart app

serviceDimensions.name: TrackMyGOALS
serviceDimensions.description: Track your savings goals on the go with this easy-to-use app. TrackMyGOALS integrates techniques that we know work for successful savers. It allows you to set, plan, track and manage your savings goals and visualize your progress towards achieving those goals. The TrackMyGOALS app helps you cultivate good savings habits and reach your dreams.

serviceDimensions.name: TrackMySPEND
serviceDimensions.description: TrackMySPEND is a free app that shows you what you are spending your money on and puts you in control.

serviceDimensions.name: Mobile Calculator
serviceDimensions.description: Have you got a financial decision to make? Access five of our most popular calculators in one app: Savings calculator, Loan calculator, Mortgage calculator, Superannuation calculator, Interest-free deal calculator

serviceDimensions.name: Money Health Check
serviceDimensions.description: The money health check helps you work out whether your finances need attention, could be better or are under control. The money health check will: Give you results tailored to your situation, Provide a list of 'to do' actions, Allow you to save or email your top 5 actions

serviceDimensions.name: NZAUConnect
serviceDimensions.description: You can now use your smartphone to quickly and easily find details on almost five million registered organisations in Australia and New Zealand with the release of the NZAUConnect app.

serviceDimensions.name: ASIC Connect Online
serviceDimensions.description: ASIC Connect is our new online service for interacting with ASIC's registers. Services available on ASIC Connect include: ASIC Connect search - for searching company, business names and self-managed superannuation fund (SMSF) auditor registers; ASIC Connect business names - for registering a business name, renewing the registration of a business name, cancelling or cancelling and transferring a business name, and updating business name details; ASIC Connect self-managed superannuation fund (SMSF) auditor - for registering as an SMSF auditor and updating SMSF auditor details.
